// AnnotationToolbar
// Toolbar strip shown above a code editor when annotations are active.
// Provides buttons to add a comment, approve all, reject all, and clear all
// annotations. Also shows the current annotation count.

FUNCTION AnnotationToolbar(annotations, onAddComment, onApproveAll, onRejectAll, onClearAll) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Renders a row of icon+label buttons.
  Add Comment button calls onAddComment with the current cursor selection.
  Approve All / Reject All call their respective handlers.
  Clear All calls onClearAll.
  Badge shows total annotation count.
